event_contents = {
  "Platform Designer" => "<!-- BEGIN app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div class=\"trix-content\">\n  <!-- BEGIN /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div>Work in a UX team of 6 designers which supports multiple business groups under<br>one holding corporation.<br>- Assigned to a business group specialising in palm oil production.<br>- Participated in requirement gathering workshops for 4 different projects.<br>- Delivered 4 Figma prototypes for projects.<br>- Proof of concept mobile &amp; web app for grading fresh fruit bunch.<br>- Web &amp; mobile app for monitoring tree health using multispectral imaging.<br>- Web &amp; mobile app for palm oil seed production.<br>- Web &amp; mobile app for R&amp;D activities.<br>- Left early from my 2-year contract to find a more flexible working environment.</div>\n<!-- END /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --></div>\n<!-- END app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb -->",
  "UI/UX Developer" => "<!-- BEGIN app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div class=\"trix-content\">\n  <!-- BEGIN /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div>Plan and manage Affin Group web consolidation project.<br>- Managed a junior UX designer who was handling multiple projects.<br>- Planned and executed UX workshops for all stakeholder levels for the<br>digitalisation of Affin Bank’s services.<br>- Participate and provide feedback for vendor’s solution presentations.<br>- Decided not to proceed after probation due to work culture mismatch.</div>\n<!-- END /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --></div>\n<!-- END app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb -->",
  "Senior Frontend Engineer" => "<!-- BEGIN app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div class=\"trix-content\">\n  <!-- BEGIN /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div>Maintain and build new features in the existing system.<br>- Technology stack: Ruby on Rails, ReactJS, SCSS.<br>- Decided to leave to take care of my then sick father.</div>\n<!-- END /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --></div>\n<!-- END app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb -->",
  "UI/UX Designer" => "<!-- BEGIN app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div class=\"trix-content\">\n  <!-- BEGIN /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div>Redesign says.com from the ground up.<br>- UX research on how to optimise reader’s and writer’s experiences for news<br>portals.<br>- Revamp says.com UI.<br>- Research on optimising workflow for the tech team across multiple news<br>portals.<br>- Left after being called back by the UI/UX team in DXC Technology. Unfortunately<br>the pandemic situation then has caused all new hirings to be frozen.</div>\n<!-- END /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --></div>\n<!-- END app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb -->",
  "UI/UX Designer" => "<!-- BEGIN app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div class=\"trix-content\">\n  <!-- BEGIN /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div>- Reports directly to the Director of Engineering / Automation.<br>- Design UI/UX for SAAS-like applications based on user stories provided by BAs.<br>- Design and build concepts for marketing pages.<br>- Get feedback from stakeholders from different regions of the world.<br>- Left due to internal politics resulting in the resignation of my reporting manager<br>and a department-wide layovers.</div>\n<!-- END /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --></div>\n<!-- END app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb -->",
  "IT Manager (acting Chief Technical Officer)" => "<!-- BEGIN app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div class=\"trix-content\">\n  <!-- BEGIN /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div>Temporary position to help a friend manage a job listing app that I built for his<br>company.<br>- Manage the IT department for the group of companies which includes one senior<br>and one junior IT executive.<br>- Managed business disaster recovery plan.<br>- Liaise with service providers and present solutions directly to the Board of<br>Directors.<br>- Successfully planned and executed a disaster recovery drill.<br>- Worked with other departments on IT related matters.</div>\n<!-- END /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --></div>\n<!-- END app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb -->",
  "Front End Web Developer / Programming Bootcamp Mentor" => "<!-- BEGIN app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div class=\"trix-content\">\n  <!-- BEGIN /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div>Mentor:<br>- Mentor students for a 9-week bootcamp.<br>- Topics covered in the boot camp includes Ruby, ActiveRecord, Basic HTML &amp;<br>CSS, Basic JavaScript, Sinatra framework and Ruby on Rails framework.<br>- Have mentored a total of 14 intakes.<br>- Main tasks was to assist students with their assignments throughout the<br>9-weeks bootcamp as well as giving lectures, doing class revisions, reviewing<br>student assessments and other classroom related tasks.<br>- Assist other departments on company activities such as live events and other<br>marketing programmes.<br>Front End Web Developer<br>- Develop and maintain in-house web applications for Next Academy.<br>- Daily tasks include building new features, review pull requests and bug fixes.<br>- Take away from the experience: Working in a team to build and maintain a Ruby<br>on Rails apps, ReactJS framework, building and working with various APIs.</div>\n<!-- END /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --></div>\n<!-- END app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb -->",
  "Lecturer" => "<!-- BEGIN app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div class=\"trix-content\">\n  <!-- BEGIN /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div>- Lecturing for diploma and foundation classes.<br>- Course subjects include Introduction to C Programming, Web Programming,<br>Introduction to Computer, Basic Computing Skills, and Multimedia subjects.<br>- Develop a new diploma programme in multimedia for accreditation submission.<br>- Supervise and coordinate student activities as well as university programs.</div>\n<!-- END /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --></div>\n<!-- END app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb -->",
  "HRA / Business Development Executive" => "<!-- BEGIN app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div class=\"trix-content\">\n  <!-- BEGIN /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div>- Worked in a project management team to build a maritime academy in Seri<br>Manjung, Perak and in Rawang, Selangor from the ground up.<br>- Coordinate with property developers and the Fire and Rescue Department<br>(Bomba) to secure premises for leasing and obtain safety certifications<br>necessary for operating a learning centre with accommodation.<br>- Assisted in the development of syllabus for a basic seamanship programme.<br>- Liaise with officials from the Marine Department of Malaysia for accreditations,<br>reporting and other official businesses.<br>- Manage day-to-day operations of the academy.<br>- Plan, supervise and coordinate student activities.</div>\n<!-- END /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --></div>\n<!-- END app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb -->",
  "L1 Technical Helpdesk Specialist" => "<!-- BEGIN app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div class=\"trix-content\">\n  <!-- BEGIN /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div>- Main role was to be the first point of contact for users experiencing technical<br>issues, including software, hardware, network, or system-related problems.<br>- Supported mainly India and Australia users, as well as users from Singapore,<br>New Zealand and Hong Kong.<br>- Diagnose and resolve technical issues which involved guiding users through<br>step-by-step solutions over the phone, using remote desktop tools to access<br>their systems, or escalating issues to higher-level support teams when<br>necessary.<br>- Document all technical support interactions, including the nature of the issue,<br>troubleshooting steps taken, and resolutions provided..<br>- Resigned from the role to join a project management opportunity.</div>\n<!-- END /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --></div>\n<!-- END app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb -->",
  "Web / Graphic Designer" => "<!-- BEGIN app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div class=\"trix-content\">\n  <!-- BEGIN /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div>- Rebranding the company’s corporate image.<br>- Involved in most of the company’s web portal projects as the lead designer.<br>- Involved in conducting and facilitating training on web design using Joomla! 1.5.</div>\n<!-- END /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --></div>\n<!-- END app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb -->",
  "Web Designer" => "<!-- BEGIN app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div class=\"trix-content\">\n  <!-- BEGIN /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div>Involved exclusively in the design phase for the development of Seri Malaysia Hotels web portal. The site has since been revamped.</div>\n<!-- END /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --></div>\n<!-- END app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb -->",
  "General Factory Worker" => "<!-- BEGIN app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div class=\"trix-content\">\n  <!-- BEGIN /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div>Worked part time at a factory while waiting for my STPM result.<br>Key takeaway: Learned the principle of Kaizen.</div>\n<!-- END /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --></div>\n<!-- END app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb -->",
  "Crew" => "<!-- BEGIN app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div class=\"trix-content\">\n  <!-- BEGIN /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div>Worked part time as floor and kitchen crew while waiting for SPM my result.<br>Key takeaway: “Clean as you go”.</div>\n<!-- END /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --></div>\n<!-- END app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb -->",
  "Freelance Digital Consultant" => "<!-- BEGIN app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div class=\"trix-content\">\n  <!-- BEGIN /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div>Providing a comprehensive range of services tailored to meet the diverse needs<br>of clients across various industries.<br>- Services spans digital marketing strategies, multimedia content creation, graphic design, video production, as well as website and web application development.</div>\n<!-- END /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --></div>\n<!-- END app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb -->",
  "Founder, Full Stack Developer & Product Designer" => "<!-- BEGIN app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div class=\"trix-content\">\n  <!-- BEGIN /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div>Plan, design and build a link management app.<br>- Tech stack: Ruby on Rails 7, Bootstrap 5.<br>- Project: https://www.gugel.my</div>\n<!-- END /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --></div>\n<!-- END app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb -->",
  "Founder, Full Stack Developer & Product Designer" => "<!-- BEGIN app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div class=\"trix-content\">\n  <!-- BEGIN /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div>Plan, design and build a debating app.<br>- Tech stack: Ruby on Rails 6, ReactJS, Bootstrap 4.<br>- The project has been archived.<br>- Writeup: https://www.behance.net/gallery/175206951/Hoojah</div>\n<!-- END /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --></div>\n<!-- END app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb -->",
  "Stage Manager" => "<!-- BEGIN app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div class=\"trix-content\">\n  <!-- BEGIN /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div>Responsible for ensuring that all elements of the production come together<br>seamlessly for the show.<br>- Worked closely with the director, designers, and production team during<br>pre-production planning stage to understand the vision for the show and assist<br>in creating a production schedule.<br>- Scheduling and running rehearsals, ensuring actors are on time and prepared,<br>coordinating with the director to facilitate the creative process, and keeping<br>detailed notes on blocking, cues, and technical requirements.<br>- Served as a central point of communication between all members of the<br>production team, including designers, crew, and performers.<br>- Keeping accurate records of all aspects of the production, including rehearsal<br>schedules, blocking diagrams, and technical cue sheets.<br>- Resigned from position mid-production due to constraints during the pandemic.</div>\n<!-- END /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --></div>\n<!-- END app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb -->",
  "Director, Co-Writer & Producer" => "<!-- BEGIN app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div class=\"trix-content\">\n  <!-- BEGIN /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --><div>Directed, co-write and produced an indie theatre play for directing class at<br>Revolution Stage.<br>- “Orang Kasar” is an adaptation of a play written by Anton Checkov called “The<br>Bear”.<br>- The production ran for 5 days with a total of 7 shows.<br>- Directed 2 main cast and 3 supporting cast members.<br>- Involved in the end-to-end production process.</div>\n<!-- END /home/rudzainy/.local/share/mise/installs/ruby/3.4.3/lib/ruby/gems/3.4.0/gems/actiontext-8.0.2/app/views/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb --></div>\n<!-- END app/views/layouts/action_text/contents/_content.html.erb -->",
